        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>The flayleaf plant is relatively common, though the mildly euphoric effects of smoking its dried leaves increase when it's sourced from plants specifically grown to produce such effects.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">A</span> Interact (Ingested, Inhaled)</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> DC 12 Fortitude</p>\n<p><strong>Onset</strong> 10 minutes</p>\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 4 hours</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> +1 item bonus to saving throws against mental effects (1 hour)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Fatigued]{Fatigued} and +1 item bonus to saving throws against mental effects (1 hour)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> fatigued and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stupefied]{Stupefied} 1 (1 hour)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 4</strong> fatigued, @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened} 2, stupefied 2 (1 hour)</p>"
